      <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="small muted"><strong>Effective date:</strong> December 29, 2025</p>

      <p>
        JayTech LLC (“JayTech,” “we,” “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we handle information
        when you visit our website or use our products and services.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Website:</strong> You can browse our website without providing personal information. If you contact us by email,
        we receive the information you choose to share (for example, your email address and message content).
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Apps and services:</strong> Our apps may collect limited information necessary to provide functionality,
        improve reliability, provide support, and maintain security. Any app-specific data practices are disclosed inside the app
        and/or in the applicable app store listing.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul class="bullets muted">
        <li>To respond to support requests and inquiries</li>
        <li>To operate, maintain, and improve our products</li>
        <li>To maintain security, prevent abuse, and comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers that help us operate our services
        (for example, hosting or analytics) subject to appropriate protections and only as necessary.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain information only as long as necessary for the purposes described above, unless a longer period is required by law.
      </p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use reasonable safeguards designed to protect information. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy questions, contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@jaytechllc.com">privacy@jaytechllc.com</a>
      </p>

      <p class="small muted">
        We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>
